title: HB Wallet
author: HB Wallet
content: Rinkeby is one of those Testnets that running parallelly to the Ethereum Mainnet.This network lays on top of Clique PoA (Proof-of-Authority) consensus protocol which protects its operation from spamming with ETH supply monitored by trusted parties.Rinkeby Faucet lets everyone claim free Ethereum on Rinkeby Testnet.Learn more about Rinkeby Faucet and Rinkeby RPC in our article
